Trivia[]

Nunu & Willump, the Boy and his Yeti
  • ▶️  "I bet, if we stayed really still we become invisible!" references Teemo's passive.
  • ▶️  "One dragon to rule them all!" references The Lord of the Rings. ("One ring to rule them all.")
Nunu, the Yeti Rider
  • ▶️  "Don't make the yeti angry. You won't like him when he's angry!" references the famous quote made by Hulk from Marvel Comics.
    • A side-by-side comparison can be seen here.
  • ▶️  "Speak softly... and ride a big yeti!" references Theodore Roosevelt ("Speak softly and carry a big stick.")
Nunu & Willump Bot
  • ▶️   Willump: "Oh, hi Marc." is a pun line for Marc 'Tryndamere' Merrill that quotes The Room (film).
  • ▶️   Willump: "Party in the front, Brambles in the back." references Joe Dirt. ("Business in the front, party in the back.")
  • ▶️   Willump: "To damage, or not to damage; let me thi- thi- thi- thi- to damage." references Hamlet. ("To be or not to be, that is the question.")
  • ▶️   Willump: "This monster makes me angry, it will not like me when I'm angry." references The Hulk's famous quote. It was carried as a reference from his old base voice-over (but not to his new base voice-over).
  • ▶️   Willump: "I have a need for speed." quotes Top Gun.
  • ▶️   Willump: "Krug life!" is a play on Thug Life.
  • ▶️   Willump: "Epic lolz." is leetspeak.
  • ▶️   Willump: "I have learned the true value of friendship. 43." references The Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy.
  • ▶️   Willump: "Rock 'em and sock 'em!" references Rock 'Em Sock 'Em Robots.
  • ▶️   Willump: "The fourth law in robotics... is punching." references Isaac Asimov's 'Robot' series.
  • ▶️   Willump: "Oh the damages! The damages!" references Heart of Darkness by Joseph Conrad. ("The horror! The horror!")
  • ▶️   Nunu: "Kawaii desu!" as a response to the Star Guardian skin line alludes to the magical girl anime-genre, while referencing the phrase's (intentionally incorrect) use by anime fandom.
  • ▶️   Willump: "I am become Death, Destroyer of Noobs." is a play on the quote by J. Robert Oppenheimer.
  • ▶️   Willump: "Doggos intensifies." uses the internet slang term for cute dogs.
  • ▶️   Nunu: "Apply wrench directly to the forehead!" references HeadOn Commercials.
  • ▶️   Willump: "Only you can prevent forest fires, by killing Red Buff." is a play on the quote by Smokey Bear.
  • ▶️   Willump: "Chickety check yourself before you get wrecked yourself." is a play on a lyric from Check Yo Self.
  • ▶️   Willump: "Rolling it down mid." references Tyler1's toxic behavior.
  • ▶️   Willump: "Jungling is so easy." references Support is so easy.
  • ▶️   Willump: "I need 6 more RP for Star Guardian Urgot." references the popular Star Guardian Urgot meme.
  • ▶️   Willump: "Can't Killean the Zillean." references Can't Killean the Zillean.
  • ▶️   Willump: "Love me some Tryndamere." is a play on Marc 'Tryndamere' Merrill's 'Love me some Regi' comment.
    • He shares this quote with ▶️   Pulsefire Caitlyn.
  • ▶️   Willump: "Another Ryze rework in 3... 2... 1." references Ryze's many reworks, which has also seen meme-status.
  • ▶️   Nunu: "Did you see all the bugs beneath that guy's armor?" references Mordekaiser's many in-game bugs.
  • ▶️   Willump: "You have dangerous eye-eye-eye-eye- guns." references ▶️   "You've got dangerous eyes, I like that" and is also a double entendre.
  • ▶️   Willump: "Now I am the Super-bot." references the skin's old quote ▶️   "When I first met you, I was the bot. Now I am the Super-bot."
  • ▶️   Willump: "Their tears are fully stacked." is a pun for stacking Tear of the Goddess.
  • There are multiple references to the old popular meme video 'pro as heck guide to master yi':
    • ▶️   Willump: "Now we have the blue circle, which looks really sweet."
    • ▶️   Willump: "Now we have the red circle, which looks sweet and helps us kill faster."
    • ▶️   Willump: "Now watch as this intense boss battle unfolds."
    • ▶️   Willump: "Brambleback is dangerous because he is red."
    • ▶️   Willump: "Not so rude now, are you?"
    • ▶️   Willump: "Those guys were worthless. Get dunked."
    • ▶️   Willump: "Master Yi, you kill fast, and are honorable."
    • ▶️   Nunu: "Watch out! He has sword boots!"'
  • The binary numbers Willump spells out during death translate to "noob":
    • ▶️   = 'n', ▶️   = 'o', ▶️   = 'b'
  • ▶️   Willump: "Rito Plsssss." might be a reference to Riot Pls which derives from a common meme used to complain to Riot Games Inc..
  • ▶️   Nunu: "Dragon down, Dream Drop Destruction!" is likely referencing Kingdom Hearts 3D: Dream Drop Distance.
  • ▶️   Willump: "Super Robot Wars, begin." references the Super Robot Wars series.
  • ▶️   Willump: "I am so awesome, I have Flash on D and F." might be a reference to the age-old Keybind Wars (Flash on D or F).
  • ▶️   Willump: "I have a bad feeling about this." quotes the running gag in Star Wars.
  • ▶️   Willump: "Welcome to the Destroyed Monster club, appreciate it alot." is a play on a quote by Imaqtpie.
  • ▶️   Willump: "Challenger is only a state of mind, Nunu. And a sweet jacket." references the 2016 Challenger jacket.
  • The pun ▶️   Willump: "I promise I won't tilt this time Nunu, I don't want you to fall off." references tilting, meaning frustration when playing games.
  • They share quotes with:
    • ▶️   ▶️   "Man, I'm good."
      • This reference was carried from his old voice-over: ▶️
